I will point out that I once got someone to replace a cursor in a trigger and the import of 45000 records into that table went from taking over 40 minutes on that server to less than a minute. Of course I had to do that because I was about to build an import that would have imported 16 million records and we estimated it would take more than 11 days to run. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
